# Building an Enterprise Lab – Windows Server 2025 + Active Directory

## Overview

This project documents the deployment of a Windows Server 2025 environment configured with Active Directory Domain Services (AD DS) and DNS to simulate an enterprise network.

The objective is to gain hands-on experience with identity management, server administration, and foundational infrastructure commonly investigated in Security Operations Center (SOC) environments.

---

## Objectives

- Install Windows Server 2025
- Configure Active Directory Domain Services (AD DS)
- Configure DNS
- Create users and groups
- Join client devices to the domain
- Prepare the environment for future security monitoring and attack simulations

---

## Environment

| Component | Role |
|----------|------|
| VMware Fusion | Virtualization |
| Windows Server 2025 | Domain Controller |
| Windows 11 | Client Machine |

